<strong>Privacy Policy</strong>
<br>
By registering on this site, the user agrees to allow this website to save a record of the input data. FurryMap.net and its administration assure you that the data collected during registration will not be shared with any third parties. The user is free to remove personal data at any time.
<br>
TL;DR: Be reasonable. Don't be toxic.
<br>
<br>
