<br>
FurryMap.net and its administration cannot be held responsible for content added by users.
<br>
FurryMap.net and its administration cannot be held responsible for harm which arises from the use of FurryMap.net. Each user is responsible for the data they publish here. Precautions notwithstanding, no guarantee is made regarding the security of data restricted from public view (e.g. "friends only").
<br>
Furthermore, FurryMap.net and its operator assume no responsibility for harm arising from hacking or other unauthorized access of data.
<br>
<br>
<strong>Usage of Data</strong>
<br>
Usage of FurryMap.net for the purposes of systematic data collection or otherwise aggregating the data therein, in whole or in part, is strictly forbidden.
