<br>
<strong>Usage Restrictions</strong>
<br>
As a user you agree not to use FurryMap.net to upload or email material that is:
illegal, threatening, abusive, harassive, defamatory, libelous, or encroaches on anothers privacy,
abusive, supercilious, intimidating, or hateful against a group or individual,
the personal information or identification of another person, used without their consent,
infringing on the rights of others,
spam of any sort,
advocating illegal activities,
an attempt to overload or cause harm to the server or other machines associated with FurryMap.net.
